title: 180 - Gumpbula
description: Today’s episode kicks off Ty Schmit welcoming the boys back with finally a full barn again! Our Canadian pal Gumpy is back and covid free! The boys then jump into the Pod FOD which is a folder that is compiled of all things around the internet. Today’s folder includes Nick’s new sweet ass tactical glasses, a couple Vin Diesel appearances, reactions to the Fresh Prince re-cast, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
